{
    "1282:0": "Pratimālakṣaṇavivaraṇam",
    "1282:1": "oṃ ..........bhagavatā yadevoktaṃ buddhākṛtau phalam |",
    "1282:2": "lakṣaṇaṃ buddhamūrttīnāṃ tadevātrāpi likhyate ||",
    "1282:3": "sarvalakṣaṇasaṃpūrṇā pratimā sukhadāyikā |",
    "1282:4": "tadvihīnā yadā yasmāt dānta(yā syādante )",
    "1282:5": "duḥkhapradāyika ||",
    "1282:6": "kiṃ tatsukham |",
    "1282:7": "tadāha - yāvantaḥ paramāṇavo bhagavatstūpeṣu bimbeṣu vā tatkarturdivi bhūtale ca niyataṃ tāvanti rājyā....rūpāsanādhisaṃpadamvinā bhuktvā ca sarvaṃ....prāpte janmajarāvipattirahitaṃ prāpnoti bauddha padam |",
    "1282:8": "ato rūpakāyasya lakṣaṇamāha - tatra samyaksambuddhānāṃ mahāvajradharāṇāñca dairghyeṇa kāyasya bāhudvayapārśvaprasāritavyāmenāpi kiṃ pramāṇam |",
    "1282:9": "svakīyāṅgulena sārddhadvādaśāṅgulastālistena pañcaviṃśatyadhikaśatāṅgulam |",
    "1282:10": "locanādidevīnāṃ dvādaśāṅgulastālastena navatālenāṣṭottaraśatāṅgulāyāmo vyāmaśca |",
    "1282:11": "bodhisattvānāñca dvādaśāṅgulairdaśatālakameva |",
    "1282:12": "kharvvalambodarakrodhānāñca ṣaṇṇavatyaṅgulamaṣṭatālena |",
    "1282:13": "lalatkrodhānāṃ tu daśatālena viṃśatyuttaraśatāṅgulāyāmavyāmābhyāṃ sarvāṅgopāṅgoditaṃ jñātavyam |",
    "1282:14": "&quot;śāsturddharmadeśanāgamanasamaye śāriputro bhagavantametadavocat - bhagavan bhagavatā vinā śrāddhaiḥ kulaputraiḥ kuladuhitṛbhiśca kathaṃ pratipattavyam |",
    "1282:15": "bhagavānāha - śāriputra !mayi gate parinirvṛte vā nyagrodhaparimaṇḍalaṃ yāvadvyāmaṃ tāvat kāyaṃ yāvatkāyaṃ tāvadvyāmaṃ pūjāsatkārārthaṃ pratimā kartavyā |",
    "1282:16": "sarvaṅgaupāṅgāvayavasthaulyalāvaṇyalālityasalīlatvaṃ saptotsadamahāhanutvaṃ chatrākāraśiraḥskandhasusaṃsthitoṣṇīṣatvādisusaṃsthānā|",
    "1282:17": "tatrāyāme vistārotsedhasandhibandhananirgamaiḥ pramāṇaṃ buddhamūrttīnāṃ bodhisattvānāṃ ca &#39;",
    "1282:18": "&#39;",
    "1282:19": "iti vacanāt |",
    "1282:20": "tatra lāvaṇyaṃ snigdhaca(dha)rmatā |",
    "1282:21": "lālityaṃ manoharatā |",
    "1282:22": "salīlatvaṃ tribhaṅgatvādiguṇena |",
    "1282:23": "saptotsadeti saptāvayavāḥ |",
    "1282:24": "utsadā ucchrayā unnatāśceti paryāyāḥ |",
    "1282:25": "katame pādadvayaṃ hastadvayaṃ skandhadvayaṃ grīvā ceti |",
    "1282:26": "aparaṃ prasiddhameva kiñcidunnatirucche(tse)dhaḥ |",
    "1282:27": "tatra caturaṅgulamuṣṇīṣaṃ keśasthānañca tathaiva lalāṭanāsikadhaścibukāntaṃ caturvādhikacaturaṅgulam |",
    "1282:28": "etenārddhatrayodaśīmātrā mukhabhāgaḥ|",
    "1282:29": "cibukaṃ dvyaṅgulaṃ bhavet |",
    "1282:30": "āyāmanirgamābhyāñcaiva caturaṅgulamiṣyate |",
    "1282:31": "caturaṅgulau kapolavākarṇamūlādvinirgatau |",
    "1282:32": "cakṣuradhaścarmaṇo&#39;",
    "1282:33": "dhobhāgā hanuḥ syāt dvyaṅgulotsedho vistārāt dvyaṃgulaśca saḥ |",
    "1282:34": "bodhisattvāpekṣaḥ so&#39;",
    "1282:35": "dhikaḥ paripūrṇaḥ syānmahāsiṃhahanuryathā |",
    "1282:36": "saṃbuddhamahāvajradharāṇāṃ kiñcidunnata ityarthaḥ |",
    "1282:37": "krodhānāṃ tu cipiṭo vistārādhikaḥ |",
    "1282:38": "adharo dvyaṅgulāyāmo nirgamotsedhamātrikaḥ |",
    "1282:39": "aṅgulyāstṛtīyabhāgo mātrika iti |",
    "1282:40": "adharamadhyaṃ bimbaphalavat |",
    "1282:41": "ekāṅgule sṛkkaṇī|",
    "1282:42": "caturaṅgulāyāmaṃ vaktraṃ yathopapannavinyāsaśca catvāriṃśaddaśanānāṃ rājadadantādikrameṇa |",
    "1282:43": "uttaroṣṭho&#39;",
    "1282:44": "ṅgulārdhaścaturyavo nirgamotsedhābhyām |",
    "1282:45": "nāsāgrā&#39;dharaṣṭāṅgulastribhāgā praṇīlākārā śmaśrumathyā |",
    "1282:46": "godhiḥ nāsādvyaṅgulavistārā sārddhāṅgulonnatā |",
    "1282:47": "buddhānāṃ kiñcidadhikā |",
    "1282:48": "atikrodhānāṃ kiñciccipiṭā pārśvanirgatā |",
    "1282:49": "arddhāṅgulasame vṛtte śrotasī|",
    "1282:50": "tasyā nāsāvaṃso(śo)",
    "1282:51": "nāsāgramavakro vistārārddhāṅgulaḥ |",
    "1282:52": "caturaṅgulaścakṣuḥ koṣaḥ |",
    "1282:53": "tanmadhyamekāṅgulaṃ vistārāt madhye dvyaṅgulam |",
    "1282:54": "bhrūvoradhastādārabhyādhaḥ paryantaṃ tryaṅguliḥ |",
    "1282:55": "cakṣuṣorantare nāsāmūlamekāṅgulaṃ bhrūcaturaṅgulāyatācāpākārā |",
    "1282:56": "arddhāṅgulavistārā madhye vajradharasya |",
    "1282:57": "krodhānāṃ tu kuṭilā |",
    "1282:58": "buddhānāṃ dhyānadṛṣṭīnāṃ dviyavavistārād dvyaṅgulaṣaṭyavādhikāyāmāccāpākāraṃ bodhisattvānāṃ tu caturyavavistārāt viṃśatiyavāyāmādutpalam |",
    "1282:59": "sarvāsāṃ śṛṅgārastrīṇāṃ aṣṭādaśayavāyāmena ṣaṭyavavistārāt matsyodarākāram |",
    "1282:60": "caturyavakaravīraṃ nāsāsamīpaṃ netrāntaḥ |",
    "1282:61": "aparanetrānto&#39;",
    "1282:62": "pāṅgaścaturyavaḥ |",
    "1282:63": "tryaṅgulaścakṣurmaṇiḥ |",
    "1282:64": "piṭakena dviyavonnataḥ |",
    "1282:65": "kālikā sātirekapañcayavapramāṇā sṛkkaṇīsūtramādṛṣṭirmadhyeputtalikā |",
    "1282:66": "sārddhaṅgulasyaiva pañcabhāgena vistāreṇaikāṅgulaṃ tārātribhāgikā&#39;",
    "1282:67": "ṅgulasya caturthāṃśaḥ prakāśito akṣiputrakaḥ |",
    "1282:68": "padmapatrākṛti[kāryo]netrakośo&#39;",
    "1282:69": "ṅgulatrayam |",
    "1282:70": "karavīrasamasūtraṃ nāsikāpuṭasya |",
    "1282:71": "tārāsamaṃ cibukaṃ sṛkkaṇī tathā |",
    "1282:72": "bhruvormadhyaṃ sārddhāṅgulam |",
    "1282:73": "tatraivorṇṇā ekāṅgulā pūrṇacandranibhā |",
    "1282:74": "nāsā urṇā uṣṇīṣasamaṃ sūtram |",
    "1282:75": "bhruvo rekhāsamau karṇṇau |",
    "1282:76": "āyāmena caturaṅgulau dvyaṅgulavistārau tatpatraṃ ca yavam |",
    "1282:77": "tayorūrdhvapatraṃ caturyavaṃ natamūcemai (muccaire)kāṅgulam |",
    "1282:78": "vilaṃ caturyavam |",
    "1282:79": "kapolakarṇacchidrayormadhye karṇṇāvarttaḥ phalikākāro dviyavaḥ |",
    "1282:80": "karṇalatā caturaṅgulī dīrghataḥ sthūlā yathā śobhanā|",
    "1282:81": "pūrvamuṣṇīṣādigrīvāparyantaṃ caturyavādhikaviṃśatyaṅgulamuktvā idānīṃ grīvādigulphādhaḥ paryantasya vibhāgaḥ kriyate |",
    "1282:82": "grīva caturaṅgulā |",
    "1282:83": "grīvāto hṛdayaṃ sārddhadvādaśāṅgulam |",
    "1282:84": "hṛdayānnābhiparyantaṃ tathā nābherāguhyaṃ sārddhadvādaśāṅgulam |",
    "1282:85": "ūruḥ pañcaviṃśatyaṅgulam,",
    "1282:86": "jaṃghāpi tathā |",
    "1282:87": "jānuḥ ṣaḍaṅgulam |",
    "1282:88": "dvyaṅgulo gulphaḥ |",
    "1282:89": "gulphādadhaścaturaṅgulameti samyaksaṃbuddhavajradharabodhisattvādīnāṃ daśatālasya kathito vibhāgaḥ |",
    "1282:90": "anyeṣāṃ tu yathāyogamunneyam |",
    "1282:91": "yathāśobhaṃ śiromaṇirvimalaḥ kāryaḥ |",
    "1282:92": "uṣṇīṣaṃ madhyasthīkṛtya dvādaśāṅgulaṃ jaṭāmakuṭaṃ vajradharasya |",
    "1282:93": "vīrāṇāṃ bodhisattvānāṃ cāṣṭāṅgulaṃ jaṭājūṭaṃ makuṭaṃ ceti viśeṣaḥ |",
    "1282:94": "daśāṅgulamiti kecit |",
    "1282:95": "uṣṇīṣādho veṣṭanena dvādaśāṅgulam |",
    "1282:96": "lalāṭoparicchatrākāram |",
    "1282:97": "nīladakṣiṇāvartamūrddhvajam |",
    "1282:98": "unnatamastakāṃ(kaṃ)",
    "1282:99": "karṇasaṃmukhapṛṣṭhaveṣṭanena dvātriṃśadaṅgulamastakam |",
    "1282:100": "grīvā cāṣṭāṅgulavistārā |",
    "1282:101": "tasyā veṣṭanaṃ caturviṃśatyaṅgulam |",
    "1282:102": "grīvāyā aṣṭāṅgulaṃ hitvā karṇasamīpe caturaṅgulena saha dvādaśāṅgulaskandhāvṛttaḥ sthāṇukṣoṇānvitaḥ |",
    "1282:103": "kṛśatārahitaskandhāt kaphoṇerurdhvaṃ viṃśatyaṅgulo bāhuḥ kaphoṇirekāṅgulā |",
    "1282:104": "kaphoṇeradhastānmaṇibandhādūrddhvaṃ prabāhuḥ ṣoḍaśāṅgulaḥ |",
    "1282:105": "ekāṅgulo maṇibandhaḥ |",
    "1282:106": "maṇibandhādadho madhyāṅgulyagraparyantaṃ dvādaśāṅgulo hastaḥ |",
    "1282:107": "evaṃ pañcāśadaṅgulam |",
    "1282:108": "bāhau madhyeveṣṭanaṃ viṃśatyaṅgulam |",
    "1282:109": "upabāhormadhyaveṣṭanaṃ ṣoḍaśāṅgulam |",
    "1282:110": "maṇibandhe veṣṭanaṃ dvādaśāṅgulam |",
    "1282:111": "maṇibandhāt saptāṅgulaṃ karatalam |",
    "1282:112": "madhyāṅgulī pañcamātrā |",
    "1282:113": "tasyāḥ parvārddhonā pradeśinī |",
    "1282:114": "anāmikā tatsamā |",
    "1282:115": "parvonā kanīyasī |",
    "1282:116": "sarvāṅgulyastriparvāḥ |",
    "1282:117": "parvārddhena nakhāstāsām |",
    "1282:118": "maṇibandhāccaturaṅgulam tyaktvā nakhāgraṃ yāvaccaturaṅgulo&#39;ṅguṣṭhaḥ |",
    "1282:119": "dviparvaḥ parvārddhena nakhaḥ |",
    "1282:120": "aṅguṣṭho vesṭanena caturaṅgulaḥ |",
    "1282:121": "aṅguṣṭhapradeśinyorantaraṃ tryaṅgulam |",
    "1282:122": "maṇibandhāt kanīyasīmūlaparyantaṃ pañcāṅgulam |",
    "1282:123": "skandhāt kakṣaparyantaṃ navāṅgulam |",
    "1282:124": "kakṣāt stanaṃ yāvat ṣaḍaṅgulam |",
    "1282:125": "uraḥpṛṣṭhayorveṣṭanaṃ ṣaṭpañcāśadaṅgulam |",
    "1282:126": "stanayormadhyaṃ sārddhadvādaśāṅgulam |",
    "1282:127": "stananābhyormadhyaṃ ṣoḍaśāṅgulam |",
    "1282:128": "nābhimārabhya vṛṣṭhena (pṛṣṭhena)",
    "1282:129": "sa[ha]nābhiṃ yāvat ṣaṭcatvāriṃśadaṅgulaṃ nābhernimūtayo ekāṅgulaṃ pariṇāhaṃ ca |",
    "1282:130": "tathā vistareṇāṣṭādaśāṅgulā kaṭiḥ sphiccau caturaṅgulau vistārāyāmau |",
    "1282:131": "urumūlayormadhyaṃ dvādaśāṅgulam |",
    "1282:132": "veṣṭanena triguṇam |",
    "1282:133": "tayormadhya āyāmena pañcāṅgulau vistāreṇa caturaṅgulau aṇḍakoṣau |",
    "1282:134": "tadupari dvyaṅgulaṃ vistāreṇa guhyaṃ dairghyeṇa dviyavādhika - ṣaḍaṅgulam |",
    "1282:135": "urumadhyaṃ veṣṭanena dvātriṃśadaṅgulam |",
    "1282:136": "jānuveṣṭanamaṣṭāviṃśatyaṅgulam |",
    "1282:137": "jaṃghāmadhyaveṣṭanaṃ caturviṃśatyaṅgulam |",
    "1282:138": "jaṃghādho veṣṭanamekaviṃśatyaṅgulam |",
    "1282:139": "pādagrantheradhaḥ pārṣṇī caturaṅgule |",
    "1282:140": "adha ūrdhvataḥ ṣaḍaṅgule |",
    "1282:141": "tiryakvistārācca pariṇāhenāṣṭādaśāṅgule |",
    "1282:142": "gulphātparato&#39;",
    "1282:143": "ṅguṣṭhanakhāgraṃ yā[va]t pādau dvādaśāṅgulau vistāreṇa ṣaḍaṅgulau |",
    "1282:144": "adha ūrdhvena dvyaṅgulavistārau pādayoḥ pārṣṇī |",
    "1282:145": "pādāṅgulyaḥ pañca dvidviparvā |",
    "1282:146": "tāsāṃ madhyaparvārddhena nakhāḥ |",
    "1282:147": "pādāṅguṣṭhaḥ pañcāṅgulaḥ pariṇāhena dairghyeṇa tryaṅgulaḥ ,",
    "1282:148": "tatsamā pradeśinī |",
    "1282:149": "tasyāḥ sārddhaparvonā madhyamā |",
    "1282:150": "tasyā aṣṭama - bhāgonānāmikā |",
    "1282:151": "tasyā apyaṣṭamabhāgonā kanīyasī |",
    "1282:152": "aṅgulya ekāṅgulonnatāḥ |",
    "1282:153": "aṅguṣṭhāgrau sārddhāṅgulonnatau |",
    "1282:154": "bahiruparipādau kūrmmapṛṣṭhasamau |",
    "1282:155": "adhastāccakrādi - bhiralaṅkṛtau |",
    "1282:156": "kukkuṭāṇḍatilākāraṃ caturasrañca maṇḍalam |",
    "1282:157": "sarvasāmānyaliṅgānāṃ mukhākṛtiścaturvidhā ||",
    "1282:158": "saṃbuddhānāṃ mahāvajradharāṇāṃ ca mukhaṃ kukkuṭāṇḍākāram |",
    "1282:159": "locanādidevakanyānāṃ tilabimbākāram |",
    "1282:160": "maitreyādimahābodhisattvānāṃ mahāvajradharavanmukham |",
    "1282:161": "kharvalambodarakrodhānāṃ maṇḍalākāraṃ vṛttamukham |",
    "1282:162": "lalitakrodhānāṃ tu bodhisattvavat |",
    "1282:163": "pretādīnāṃ tu caturasraṃ mukham |",
    "1282:164": "lāvaṇyadarśanaṃ mukhadvayam |",
    "1282:165": "caturasramaṇḍalaṃ mukhadvayaṃ vikṛtākāram |",
    "1282:166": "same dṛṣṭi(ṣṭhī)",
    "1282:167": "prasannāsye saumyasnigdhāvalokane |",
    "1282:168": "sārddhena dainyayukte&#39;",
    "1282:169": "dhaḥ kartavye sarvadarśinām ||iti |",
    "1282:170": "locanādi yoginīnāṃ uṣṇīṣaguhyorupṛṣṭhaveṣṭanāt daśāṅgulena saha pīnaghanakucau |",
    "1282:171": "nābhāvaveṣṭanāt daśabhāgaṃ hitvā kaṭisthalaṃ pīnaṃ kartavyam |",
    "1282:172": "bodhisattvamānāduraso daśabhāgena guhyāṃśena ca vīriṇīnā(nāṃ)",
    "1282:173": "kucayugmaṃ |",
    "1282:174": "kaṭisthalaṃ tu pūrvavat |",
    "1282:175": "kākāsyādīnāṃ tattāladvayena stanādau pīnatā |",
    "1282:176": "bhagavataḥ śrīsaṃvarasya pūrvakṛtalakṣaṇe mukhakṣetre caturyavaṃ hitvā dvādaśabhāgikavistāre adhaḥ koṇayorekasārddhadvisārddhadvibhāgaharaṇavarttanāt bhagavato mūlavāmadakṣiṇapaścimavaktrāṇi |",
    "1282:177": "bhagavato dakṣiṇakhagāṇḍamukhavad vajravārāhīkhaṇḍarohārūpiṇīdevakanyānāṃ ca paścimamukhavattilabimbākāraṃ ḍākinyāḥ pūrvamukhavat lāmāyāḥ vāmamukhavat cūtābhaṃ vīravīreśvarīṇāñca |",
    "1282:178": "kākāsyādīnāṃ kākādimukhameva bhagavato vāmadakṣiṇamukhaṃ ca kurvaddhasitatrasitabubhukṣitānāmiveti viśeṣaḥ |",
    "1282:179": "indra - īśānavāyuvaruṇa - upendrapitāmahā navatālāḥ khagāṇḍamukhāḥ |",
    "1282:180": "vemacitrinairṛtiṣaṭtālāḥ krodhasvabhāvāḥ |",
    "1282:181": "kuberānalau lalitakharvāvaṣṭatālau khagāṇḍamukhau |",
    "1282:182": "saumyagrahāḥ sūryaśca śakravanmānamānitāḥ |",
    "1282:183": "krūrāḥ krodhasvabhāvāḥ |",
    "1282:184": "arddhakāyo rāhuḥ |",
    "1282:185": "adhaḥkāyanāgākāraḥ ketuḥ |",
    "1282:186": "sarvanāgā navatālā khagāṇḍamukhāḥ |",
    "1282:187": "vaṭuvāmanaherambaḥ kartavyaḥ pañcatālikaḥ |",
    "1282:188": "tatra tālaikena mukhaḥ grīvāta āguhyaṃ yāvattāladvayena guhyataḥ pādatalaṃ yāvattāladvayeneti pañcatālam |",
    "1282:189": "tatra saṃbuddhāḥ karuṇābhūtaśāntarasopetāḥ vajradharamukhaṃ sarvaśarīraṃ navarasarasāviṣṭam |",
    "1282:190": "bodhisattvādayastu śṛṅgārarasādhikāḥ iti prastāraḥ kathitaḥ ||",
    "1282:191": "|| iti samyaksambuddhabhāṣitaṃ pratimālakṣaṇavivaraṇaṃ samāptam ||",
    "1282:192": "svabhāvāḥ |",
    "1282:193": "arddhakāyo rāhuḥ |",
    "1282:194": "adhaḥkāyanāgākāraḥ ketuḥ |",
    "1282:195": "sarvanāgā navatālā khagāṇḍamukhāḥ |",
    "1282:196": "vaṭuvāmanaherambaḥ kartavyaḥ pañcatālikaḥ |",
    "1282:197": "tatra tālaikena mukhaḥ grīvāta āguhyaṃ yāvattāladvayena guhyataḥ pādatalaṃ yāvattāladvayeneti pañcatālam |",
    "1282:198": "tatra saṃbuddhāḥ karuṇābhūtaśāntarasopetāḥ vajradharamukhaṃ sarvaśarīraṃ"
}